title: Ground News - Ashley Benson Gives Birth, Welcomes First Baby With Husband Brandon Davis
text: Ashley Benson and Brandon Davis have welcomed their first child together. The couple announced they were engaged in July of last year after less than a year of dating. They have not released any further information about the newest addition to their family. They were spotted shopping for baby supplies in Beverley Hills, California, in November.
